装修的优美与舒适，体验科学技术的发展给人们生活带来的舒适与方便。</p>            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            2、了解房屋装修的特点，体现人们生活水平的提高，居住条件的改善。</p>            </td>            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"90\\\\\" height=\\\\\"182\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: medium none; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0pt; border-left: medium none; width: 68.15pt; padding-top: 0pt; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid\\\\\">            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            1、利用墙角创设&ldquo;建材城&rdquo;将幼儿带的照片展示出来。</p>            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            2、利用小墙壁展示&ldquo;我们漂亮的家&rdquo;的照片。</p>            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            3、将幼儿提出的关于装修的问题展示出来。</p>            </td>            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"58\\\\\" height=\\\\\"182\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: medium none; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0pt; border-left: medium none; width: 43.5pt; padding-top: 0pt; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid\\\\\">            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            师幼在主体活动中逐渐创设&ldquo;我们漂亮的家&rdquo;的主题墙饰。</p>            </td>            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"110\\\\\" height=\\\\\"182\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: medium none; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0pt; border-left: medium none; width: 82.65pt; padding-top: 0pt; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid\\\\\">            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            美工区：制作装修材料。（灯、瓷砖、装饰窗帘等）粉刷房子。</p>            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            建筑区：搭建漂亮的房子。</p>            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            娃娃家：根据自己的意愿摆放家具。</p>            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            益智区：拚图：漂亮的房子。</p>            </td>            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"82\\\\\" height=\\\\\"182\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: medium none; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0pt; border-left: medium none; width: 62pt; padding-top: 0pt; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid\\\\\">            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            1、请家长为自己家中有特点的装修进行拍照。</p>            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            2、带幼儿参观建材城并拍照。</p>            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            3、向家长介绍本主题活动的内容。</p>            </td>            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"101\\\\\" height=\\\\\"182\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: medium none; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0pt; border-left: medium none; width: 75.75pt; padding-top: 0pt; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid\\\\\">            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            1、歌曲《粉刷匠》</p>            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><br />            2、录像：了解装修工人的辛苦及装修</p>            </td>        </tr>    </tbody></table>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('4280','226','无','','<p><strong>活动由来：</strong><br />幼儿进入中班之后，对周围事物的好奇心日益增加，有的幼儿发现每到一个季节我们都会换不同的衣服，衣服成为了幼儿在活动之余经常谈论的话题，我们就从幼儿的这一兴趣点出发，设计了这一主题活动。</p><p><table height=\\\\\"200\\\\\" cellspacing=\\\\\"0\\\\\" cellpadding=\\\\\"0\\\\\" width=\\\\\"550\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" border=\\\\\"0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0pt; width: 550px; padding-top: 0pt; border-collapse: collapse; height: 200px; mso-table-layout-alt: fixed\\\\\">    <tbody>        <tr>            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"99\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0pt; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; width: 74.45pt; padding-top: 0pt; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-left-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)\\\\\">            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\">活动目标<o:p></o:p></p>            </td>            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"69\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-bottom: 0pt; border-left: medium none; width: 52.45pt; padding-top: 0pt; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; mso-border-top-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-left-alt: none; mso-border-right-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0); mso-border-bottom-alt: 0.5000pt solid rgb(0,0,0)\\\\\">            <p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center\\\\\"><br />            问题板<o:p></o:p></p>            </td>            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"49\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 0.5pt solid; padding-right: 5.4